int countHomogenous(String s) {
    int res = 0, count = 1, mod = 1000000007;
    for (int i = 1; i < s.length(); ++i) {
        count = (s.charAt(i) == s.charAt(i - 1)) ? count + 1 : 1;
        res = (res + count) % mod;
    }
    return res;
}
```

